name: Edge Champagne Dial Two Toned Stainless Steel Strap Watch
spec_1: This analog watch for men features a champagne, rectangular dial housed in a stainless steel case. The case is fitted with a crown that lets you adjust the time. The dial has two plain hands, numeral markings at quarter intervals and slanted markings at five-minute intervals to ease time reading. Its strap is made of stainless steel. Equipped with 3 ATM water-resistant depth, this timepiece comes with a 24 month warranty.
spec_15: WARRANTY DETAILS - This watch offers 24 months warranty on the Movement and 12 months warranty on the Battery from the date of purchase.
